{"tid":477011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者問何志平為人 董建華：食咗飯未？","createTime":"2017-11-22T14:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T04:29:41.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4e5b1c62dc048749e047aa3b9190918164f54de0","tid":477011,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:11:22.000Z","msg":"前民政事務局局長何志平涉貪污在美國被捕，其出任常務副主席的「中華能源基金委員會」，是內地民企「中國華信能源有限公司」旗下的民間智庫，外界盛傳前特首董建華是基金會幕後推手，而做過董建華高級特別助理的路祥安為基金會副秘書長。董建華今出席團結香港基金3周年晚宴，在宴會前被問到，對何志平為人有何看法時，他僅指「陣間聽我講嘢」，又向記者微笑揮手，問候「食咗飯未呀」。"},{"pid":"804f7ba64af779bfc755329b8d37099965aced25","tid":477011,"uid":7369,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"老撚到眼又曚耳又聾"},{"pid":"fc03678693df924fc679a3473da07f3a1e963366","tid":477011,"uid":24730,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:17:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老撚到眼又曚耳又聾</blockquote><br />\n佢一向風格係咁，唔關老事"},{"pid":"47e6aa9919ae04f8a8795fb7497ee8c670fac11d","tid":477011,"uid":3773,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:18:20.000Z","msg":"又係呢句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聞到棺材香未呀老懵懂？"},{"pid":"fd75b3eaf1aed99543880adac762f9347427b6ad","tid":477011,"uid":106336,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:18:28.000Z","msg":"老董：<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/c/c6/Tungword1.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20071111133806\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fc%2Fc6%2FTungword1.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20071111133806&h=e898373b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5babf754c054d9bf41279044188298a52a08fe7","tid":477011,"uid":2054,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T14:19:21.000Z","msg":"何志平....（望地下幾秒）...已經...唔存在啦"},{"pid":"d1b1d3d6134492bd91ac0977f52d406144e28b35","tid":477011,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedB